includedLibraries.cql:
library DateUtils version '1.0.0'

using FHIR version '4.0.1'

include FHIRHelpers version '1.0.0' called FHIRHelpers


/**
@type: {urn:hl7-org:elm-types:r1}DateTime
*/
define function "DateTimeToDate"(Value DateTime):
	DateTime(year from Value, month from Value, day from Value, 0, 0, 0, 0, timezoneoffset from Value)

/**
@type: {urn:hl7-org:elm-types:r1}Integer
*/
define function "YearsSinceDate"(fromDate DateTime):
	years between DateTimeToDate(fromDate) and DateTimeToDate(Today())

define function "LengthInDays" (Value Interval<DateTime>):
	difference in days between start of Value and end of Value
